results.description:
Live, Love, Laugh Pewter Pocket Buddy Amulet - Absolutely gorgeous workmanship and detail are evident in this lovely solid pewter treasure that could be the start of an heirloom collection. It measures 1" inches tall by .75" wide. Made from lead-free, zinc based pewter. A must for collectors of fine fantasy objects, a great gift to say 'I love you' to someone special, the start of an heirloom collection, the possibilities are as endless as your imagination! Great for carrying around for luck, displaying when that little extra touch of love is needed. Sometimes we just need a reminder of the important things in life.

Pocket buddies are miniature characters or symbols that you can carry around with you, or put in an amulet bag with other special items, like polished stones or crystal points. The idea of the amulet bag is to place in it items specific to the person you are gifting it to, or specific to you. A typical amulet bag can contain stones, seeds, a lock of hair, small things that represent something special to the person. Please see my other amulets and polished stones to make up a perfect amulet bag for you or your loved one in need of a little affirmation.
